This shows a DNS server that helps in resolving the corresponding host ip adress of any domain name, the clients system, as well as a web server, application server, application files and application database.

Immediately hte user types any we address on his or her nrowser the DOmain name system translates it into an ip address, the clients device goes further to establish a http connection with the server.

The web server recieves a request and passes to the application server which handles the logics and decides on data to be sent to the user.

 in this setup the application server can get rsults from the database or sumply serve a static page as the case may be.
The database on the other hand stores all website data in a way it can be easily retrieved, indexed and searched. databases can assits in dynamic output as on page can request of die
